description: Convert a HuggingFace repo's pytorch_model.bin to model.safetensors for flodl-hf

# Argv passes through to the Python script (entry: commands forward argv;
# run: commands do not — see feedback_cli_docs_three_contexts).
#
# Writes /workspace/.hf-cache/flodl-converted/<repo_id>/model.safetensors, which
# flodl-hf/src/hub.rs::fetch_safetensors checks before falling back to the Hub.

docker: hf-parity
entry: python /workspace/flodl-hf/scripts/convert_bin_to_safetensors.py
